General.Name: Works co uk PLC
General.Description: TheWorks.co.uk plc operates as a retailer of gifts, arts, crafts, toys, books, and stationery products in the United Kingdom and Ireland. The company sells its products through a network of stores, as well as through its online platform. The company was founded in 1981 and is based in Birmingham, the United Kingdom.
